    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_TurnOnMeter",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to activate a meter associated with a specific account in a billing system. It performs several checks to ensure the validity of the operation, updates the meter's status, and logs the transaction. The procedure also handles errors gracefully by using a TRY-CATCH block to manage exceptions and ensure data integrity through transaction management."
        }
